    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a definitive example of mechanical purity, powered by the 3.8L flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and an integrated dry-sump lubrication system. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping characteristics across the rev range. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a mechanical limited-slip differential, providing exceptional longitudinal and lateral grip. This specimen shows zero DME over-revs in high-stress ranges and retains its factory-applied finish with no evidence of panel replacement or oxidation. The interior maintains its original tactile integrity with no bolster wear or switchgear delamination. A superlative choice for the discerning collector demanding a turn-key, high-performance icon.",
      "price": 48500.0,
